file.name: openapi-restaurant-1.0.0.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.3"
info:
  title: "Restaurant Service API"
  description: "Restaurant Service API. This is a simple service providing CRUD functionality for Restaurant meta data."
  version: "1.0.0"
servers:
  - url: "https://localhost:8080"
paths:
  /restaurants:
    get:
      summary: "GET restaurants"
      operationId: "getRestaurants"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
    post:
      summary: "POST restaurants"
      operationId: "saveRestaurant"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
  /restaurants/{id}:
    get:
      summary: "GET restaurants/{id}"
      operationId: "restaurant"
      parameters:
        - name: "id"
          in: "path"
          required: true
          schema:
            type: "string"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
    put:
      summary: "PUT restaurants/{id}"
      operationId: "replaceRestaurant"
      parameters:
        - name: "id"
          in: "path"
          required: true
          schema:
            type: "string"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
    delete:
      summary: "DELETE restaurants/{id}"
      operationId: "deleteRestaurant"
      parameters:
        - name: "id"
          in: "path"
          required: true
          schema:
            type: "string"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "OK"
